             was indicted for <rs id="t18030216-35-off197" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030216-35-off197" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030216-35-off197" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18030216-35-cd198" type="crimeDate">9th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030216-35-off197 t18030216-35-cd198"></join>, two pewter pint pots, value 16d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18030216-35-victim214" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Ilet
                  <interp inst="t18030216-35-victim214" type="surname" value="Ilet"></interp>
