                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030216-35-defend212 t18030216-35-punish203"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
